description:
This property is a 1,120 Sqft studio penthouse with 1 bathroom that is available for rent. It is part of the Tijani Raja Dewa - Apartments project in Panji, Kelantan and was completed in Mar 2023. You can rent this penthouse long term for RM550 per month.
Sky River Front Service Apartment 1 Bed 1 Bath Studio/Condo
